INSERT INTO `icerik` VALUES (15,2,'2022-03-20',NULL,'GÃ¶kÃ§e Ã–zel kimdir ?','gke-zel-kimdir',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Ä°stanbul &Uuml;niversitesi CerrahpaÅŸa Ä°ngilizce TÄ±p Fak&uuml;ltesi Mezunuyum. DÄ±ÅŸkapÄ± YÄ±ldÄ±rÄ±m BeyazÄ±t EÄŸitim ve AraÅŸtÄ±rma Hastanesi Kulak Burun BoÄŸaz KliniÄŸinde UzmanlÄ±k EÄŸitimimi TamamladÄ±m.</p>\n\n<p>2013-2021 yÄ±llarÄ± arasÄ±nda KÄ±rÄ±kkale &Uuml;niversitesi TÄ±p Fak&uuml;ltesi Kulak Burun BoÄŸaz Anabilim DalÄ±nda &Ouml;ÄŸretim &Uuml;yesi olarak &ccedil;alÄ±ÅŸtÄ±m. 2015 YÄ±lÄ±nda Do&ccedil;ent, 2021 yÄ±lÄ±nda Profes&ouml;r oldum oldum.</p>\n\n<p>T&uuml;rkiye Y&uuml;z Plastik Cerrahi DerneÄŸi Y&ouml;netim Kurulu ve Avrupa Fasiyal Plastik Cerrahi DerneÄŸi &uuml;yesiyim. Complications in Medical Aesthetic Collaborative (CMAC) derneÄŸi uluslararasÄ± danÄ±ÅŸma kurulundayÄ±m. Ulusal ve uluslararasÄ± dergilerde yayÄ±nlanmÄ±ÅŸ 100&rsquo;&uuml;n &uuml;zerinde makalem mevcut olup H indeksim 12&rsquo;dir.</p>\n\n<p>Mesleki pratiÄŸinde kulak burun boÄŸaz branÅŸÄ±nÄ±n her alanÄ±nda hastalarÄ±na hizmet vermektedir.</p>\n','','Who is Gokce Ozel?','who-is-gokce-ozel',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>I am a graduate of Istanbul University Cerrahpaşa English Faculty of Medicine. I completed my residency training at Dışkapı Yıldırım Beyazıt Training and Research Hospital Otorhinolaryngology Clinic.</p><p>Between 2013 and 2021, I worked as a faculty member at Kırıkkale University Faculty of Medicine, Department of Otorhinolaryngology. I became an Associate Professor in 2015 and a Professor in 2021.</p><p>I am a board member of the Facial Plastic Surgery Association of Turkey and a member of the European Academy of Facial Plastic Surgery. I serve on the international advisory board of the Complications in Medical Aesthetic Collaborative (CMAC). I have over 100 articles published in national and international journals, with an H-index of 12.</p><p>In my professional practice, I provide services to my patients in all areas of the otorhinolaryngology branch.</p>','','Кто такая Гёкче Озель?',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Я выпускница медицинского факультета Стамбульского университета Джеррахпаша. Прошла специализацию в клинике оториноларингологии учебно-исследовательской больницы Дышкапы Йылдырым Беязыт.</p><p>С 2013 по 2021 год я работала преподавателем кафедры оториноларингологии медицинского факультета университета Кырыккале. В 2015 году стала доцентом, а в 2021 году — профессором.</p><p>Являюсь членом правления Турецкой ассоциации эстетической хирургии лица и Европейской ассоциации лицевой эстетической хирургии. Нахожусь в международном консультативном совете ассоциации Complications in Medical Aesthetic Collaborative (CMAC). Имею более 100 статей, опубликованных в национальных и международных журналах, мой индекс Хирша — 12.</p><p>В своей профессиональной практике я оказываю услуги пациентам во всех областях оториноларингологии.</p>','','من هي جوكتشه أوزيل؟',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p>أنا خريجة كلية الطب باللغة الإنجليزية في جامعة إسطنبول جراح باشا. أكملت تدريبي التخصصي في عيادة الأنف والأذن والحنجرة بمستشفى دِشكابي يلدريم بيازيد للتدريب والبحوث.</p><p>بين عامي 2013 و 2021، عملت كعضو هيئة تدريس في قسم الأنف والأذن والحنجرة بكلية الطب جامعة كيريكالي. أصبحت أستاذًا مشاركًا في عام 2015 وأستاذًا في عام 2021.</p><p>أنا عضو في مجلس إدارة الجمعية التركية لجراحة تجميل الوجه وعضو في الأكاديمية الأوروبية لجراحة تجميل الوجه. أنا أيضًا عضو في المجلس الاستشاري الدولي لجمعية المضاعفات في التعاون الطبي التجميلي (CMAC). لدي أكثر من 100 مقال منشور في مجلات وطنية ودولية، ومعامل هيرش الخاص بي هو 12.</p><p>في ممارستي المهنية، أقدم خدمات لمرضاي في جميع مجالات تخصص الأنف والأذن والحنجرة.</p>','','Qui est Gökçe Özel?',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Je suis diplômée de la faculté de médecine (section anglaise) de l\'Université d\'Istanbul Cerrahpaşa. J\'ai effectué ma spécialisation à la clinique d\'oto-rhino-laryngologie de l\'hôpital de formation et de recherche Dışkapı Yıldırım Beyazıt.</p><p>De 2013 à 2021, j\'ai travaillé comme membre du corps professoral au département d\'ORL de la faculté de médecine de l\'Université Kırıkkale. Je suis devenue professeure associée en 2015 et professeure titulaire en 2021.</p><p>Je suis membre du conseil d\'administration de la Société Turque de Chirurgie Plastique et Esthétique Faciale et membre de l\'Académie Européenne de Chirurgie Plastique Faciale. Je fais partie du conseil consultatif international de la Complications in Medical Aesthetic Collaborative (CMAC). J\'ai plus de 100 articles publiés dans des revues nationales et internationales et mon indice h est de 12.</p><p>Dans ma pratique professionnelle, je propose des services dans tous les domaines liés à l\'ORL.</p>','','Wer ist Gökçe Özel?','wer-ist-gke-zel',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Ich bin Absolventin der medizinischen Fakultät der Universität Istanbul, Cerrahpaşa (Englischer Zweig). Meine Facharztausbildung habe ich an der Klinik für Hals-Nasen-Ohren-Heilkunde des Ausbildungs- und Forschungskrankenhauses Dışkapı Yıldırım Beyazıt abgeschlossen.</p><p>Zwischen 2013 und 2021 habe ich als Dozentin an der medizinischen Fakultät der Universität Kırıkkale in der Abteilung für HNO gearbeitet. 2015 wurde ich außerordentliche Professorin und 2021 Professorin.</p><p>Ich bin Vorstandsmitglied der Türkischen Gesellschaft für Ästhetische Gesichtschirurgie und Mitglied der Europäischen Gesellschaft für Ästhetische Gesichtschirurgie (EAFPS). Zudem bin ich Mitglied des internationalen Beirats des Complications in Medical Aesthetic Collaborative (CMAC). Ich habe über 100 Artikel in nationalen und internationalen Fachzeitschriften veröffentlicht, mein H-Index liegt bei 12.</p><p>In meiner beruflichen Praxis betreue ich Patienten in allen Bereichen der HNO-Heilkunde.</p>','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'560f90dee99bf2a65f1420220320eyalcinfb244a80aa5cd543d597',1,'2022-03-20 14:22:06',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(16,40,'2022-03-20',NULL,'Neler YapÄ±yoruz','neler-yapyoruz',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Burun EstetiÄŸi</li>\r\n	<li>Kulak EstetiÄŸi</li>\r\n	<li>Y&uuml;z Germe EstetiÄŸi</li>\r\n	<li>Boyun Germe EstetiÄŸi</li>\r\n	<li>G&ouml;z EstetiÄŸi</li>\r\n	<li>&Ccedil;ene EstetiÄŸi</li>\r\n	<li>Endoskopik Sin&uuml;s Cerrahisi</li>\r\n	<li>Sin&uuml;s Tedavisi</li>\r\n	<li>Migren Tedavisi</li>\r\n	<li>Dolgu&nbsp;UygulamalarÄ±</li>\r\n	<li>Ozon UygulamalarÄ±</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','','What We Do','what-we-do',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Nose Aesthetics<br />\r\nEar Aesthetics<br />\r\nFace Lift Aesthetics<br />\r\nNeck Lift Aesthetics<br />\r\nEye Aesthetics<br />\r\nChin Aesthetics<br />\r\nEndoscopic Sinus Surgery<br />\r\nSinus Treatment<br />\r\nMigraine Treatment<br />\r\nFilling&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ù…Ø§Ø°Ø§ Ù†ÙØ¹Ù„','content-1770827144-5077',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¬ÙŠÙˆØ¨ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠØ© Ø¨Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù†Ø¸Ø§Ø±&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø´Ø¯ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ (ÙØ§ÙŠØ³Ù„ÙŠÙØª)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø³ÙƒÙˆØ¨ ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø°Ù† (Ø§ÙˆØªÙˆØ¨Ù„Ø§Ø³ØªÙŠ)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø±Ù‚Ø¨Ø©&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø¹ÙŠÙ† Ø§Ù„Ù„ÙˆØ²&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬ÙÙ†&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø­Ø´Ùˆ&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø´Ø¯ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ Ø¨Ø­Ø¨Ù„ (Ø­Ø²Ø§Ù… ÙØ±Ù†Ø³ÙŠ )&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬ Ø§Ù„ØµØ¯Ø§Ø¹ Ø§Ù„Ù†ØµÙÙŠ&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø´ÙØ· Ø¯Ù‡ÙˆÙ† Ø§Ù„Ø°Ù‚Ù†&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„ÙÙƒ (Ù…ÙŠÙ†ØªÙˆØ¨Ù„Ø§Ø³ØªÙŠ)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡Ø§Øª ØªÙ‚Ø´ÙŠØ± Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ù„Ø¯ (Ø§Ù„ØªÙ‚Ø´ÙŠØ± Ø§Ù„ÙƒÙŠÙ…ÙŠØ§Ø¦ÙŠ)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ù†Ø¯Ø¨Ø§Øª (Ù…Ø±Ø§Ø¬Ø¹Ø© Ø§Ù„Ù†Ø¯Ø¨Ø©)</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Was machen wir?','was-machen-wir',1,NULL,NULL,'<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Rhinoplastik</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Ohrenschmalz (Otoplastik)</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Gesichts-Hals-&Auml;sthetik</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Augenlid&auml;sthetik</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Augenbrauen Heben</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Lippen&auml;sthetik</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Facelift</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Kinn&auml;sthetik</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>FuÌˆllung</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'44a1b353e234c3d9e1d520220320eyalcin889b27d8733957315ee7',1,'2022-03-20 14:57:06',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(17,41,'2022-03-20',NULL,'Prof. Dr. GÃ¶kÃ§e Ã–zel KliniÄŸi','prof-dr-gke-zel-klinii',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Y&uuml;z EstetiÄŸi hakkÄ±nda detaylÄ± bilgi almak i&ccedil;in l&uuml;tfen iletiÅŸim kanallarÄ± &uuml;zerinden bize ulaÅŸÄ±n.</p>\r\n','','Prof. Dr. Gokce Private Clinic','prof-dr-gokce-private-clinic',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>For detailed information about Facial Aesthetics, please contact us via communication channels.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ø¹ÙŠØ§Ø¯Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø±ÙˆÙÙŠØ³ÙˆØ± Ø¯ÙƒØªÙˆØ± Ø¬ÙˆÙƒØ´Ù‡ Ø§ÙˆØ²ÙŠÙ„ ','content-1770827144-7525',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ù„Ù„Ø­ØµÙˆÙ„ Ø¹Ù„Ù‰ Ù…Ø¹Ù„ÙˆÙ…Ø§Øª Ù…ÙØµÙ„Ø© Ø­ÙˆÙ„ Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ ØŒ ÙŠØ±Ø¬Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ø§ØªØµØ§Ù„ Ø¨Ù†Ø§ Ø¹Ø¨Ø± Ù‚Ù†ÙˆØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø§ØªØµØ§Ù„.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'960f9d3fa7e6325f814220220320eyalcin7d7b14d9461ddae47bec',1,'2022-03-20 15:08:09',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(18,45,'2022-03-20',NULL,'YÃ¼z EstetiÄŸi mi dÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼nÃ¼yorsunuz ?','yz-estetii-mi-dnyorsunuz',1,NULL,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align:center\">Rinoloji, otoloji, baÅŸ ve boyun cerrahisi alanlarÄ±nda &ccedil;ok sayÄ±da klinik ve akademik &ccedil;alÄ±ÅŸmasÄ± bulunan Prof. Dr. G&ouml;k&ccedil;e &Ouml;zel&rsquo;in asÄ±l ilgi alanÄ± y&uuml;z estetik cerrahisidir.&nbsp;Klinik pratiÄŸinde &ouml;zellikle y&uuml;z gen&ccedil;leÅŸtirmeye y&ouml;nelik, y&uuml;ze uyumlu ve doÄŸal bir g&ouml;r&uuml;n&uuml;m elde etmeyi ama&ccedil;layan m&uuml;dahaleler ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirmeyi seven G&ouml;k&ccedil;e &Ouml;zel bu anlamda sayÄ±sÄ±z y&uuml;z ve boyun germe, gÄ±dÄ± liposuction, rinoplasti, blefaroplasti, kaÅŸ kaldÄ±rma ve alÄ±n germe, kep&ccedil;e kulak estetiÄŸi, &ccedil;ene estetiÄŸi, botulinum toksin ve dolgu uygulamalarÄ±, mezoterapi, lipoliz mezoterapisi ve ip estetiÄŸi iÅŸlemleri ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirmiÅŸtir.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ù‡Ù„ ØªÙÙƒØ± ÙÙŠ Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ØŸ','content-1770827144-2261',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø±ÙˆÙÙŠØ³ÙˆØ± Ø¯ÙƒØªÙˆØ± Ø¬ÙˆÙƒØ´Ù‡ Ø§ÙˆØ²ÙŠÙ„ ØŒ Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ Ù„Ø¯ÙŠÙ‡Ø§ Ø§Ù„ÙƒØ«ÙŠØ± Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø¯Ø±Ø§Ø³Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø³Ø±ÙŠØ±ÙŠØ© ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø£ÙƒØ§Ø¯ÙŠÙ…ÙŠØ© ÙÙŠ Ù…Ø¬Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª Ø·Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø£Ø°Ù† ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø­Ù†Ø¬Ø±Ø© ÙˆØ¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø±Ø£Ø³ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø±Ù‚Ø¨Ø© ØŒ Ù‡ÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø§Ù‡ØªÙ…Ø§Ù… Ø§Ù„Ø±Ø¦ÙŠØ³ÙŠ Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡. Ø¬ÙˆÙƒØ´Ù‡ Ø§ÙˆØ²ÙŠÙ„ ØŒ Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ­Ø¨ Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø§Ù„ØªØ¯Ø®Ù„Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªÙ‡Ø¯Ù Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ ØªØ­Ù‚ÙŠÙ‚ Ù…Ø¸Ù‡Ø± Ù…ØªÙ†Ø§ØºÙ… ÙˆØ·Ø¨ÙŠØ¹ÙŠ ØŒ Ø®Ø§ØµØ© Ù„ØªØ¬Ø¯ÙŠØ¯ Ø´Ø¨Ø§Ø¨ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ ÙÙŠ Ù…Ù…Ø§Ø±Ø³ØªÙ‡Ø§ Ø§Ù„Ø³Ø±ÙŠØ±ÙŠØ© ØŒ Ù„Ø¯ÙŠÙ‡Ø§ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø¯ÙŠØ¯ Ù…Ù† Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø´Ø¯ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø±Ù‚Ø¨Ø© ØŒ ÙˆØ´ÙØ· Ø¯Ù‡ÙˆÙ† Ø§Ù„Ø°Ù‚Ù† ØŒ ÙˆØ¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ØŒ ÙˆØ¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¬ÙÙ† ØŒ ÙˆØ±ÙØ¹ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø¨ ÙˆØ´Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø¨Ù‡Ø© ØŒ ÙˆØ¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø°Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø§Ø±Ø²Ø© ØŒ ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø°Ù‚Ù† ØŒ&nbsp; ØªÙ… Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ ØªØ·Ø¨ÙŠÙ‚Ø§Øª ØªÙˆÙƒØ³ÙŠÙ† Ø§Ù„Ø¨ÙˆØªÙˆÙ„ÙŠÙ†ÙˆÙ… ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø­Ø´Ùˆ ØŒ Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙŠØ²ÙˆØ«ÙŠØ±Ø§Ø¨ÙŠ ØŒ Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙŠØ²ÙˆØ«ÙŠØ±Ø§Ø¨ÙŠ ØªØ­Ù„Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ø¯Ù‡Ù† ØŒ ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø®ÙŠÙˆØ·.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Denken Sie Ã¼ber GesichtsÃ¤sthetik nach?','denken-sie-ber-gesichtssthetik-nach',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Nach vielen klinischen und akademischen Studien in den Bereichen Rhinologie, Otologie, Kopf- und Halschirurgie liegt das Hauptinteresse von Prof. Dr. G&ouml;k&ccedil;e &Ouml;zel in der &auml;sthetischen Gesichtschirurgie.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&ouml;k&ccedil;e &Ouml;zel, die in ihrer klinischen Praxis gerne Eingriffe vor allem zur Gesichtsverj&uuml;ngung vornimmt und ein harmonisches und nat&uuml;rliches Erscheinungsbild anstrebt, hat in diesem Sinne zahlreiche &auml;sthetische Gesichts- und Halslifting-Operationen, Wangenfettabsaugung, Rhinoplastik, Blepharoplastik, Augenbrauenlifting und Stirnlifting, Abstehende Ohr&auml;sthetik, Kinn&auml;sthetik, Botulinumtoxin- und F&uuml;llungsanwendungen, Mesotherapie, Lipolyse, Mesotherapie und Faden&auml;sthetik durchgef&uuml;hrt.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'b0503f383a6a7bd328be20220320eyalcinca37b61b0cc20b946534',1,'2022-03-20 17:43:08',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(19,43,'2022-03-20',NULL,'Revizyon Rinoplasti','revizyon-rinoplasti',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Revizyon Rinoplasti, daha &ouml;nce ameliyat olmuÅŸ fakat burundaki ÅŸekil bozukluklarÄ± ile nefes alma problemleri devam eden ve bu sorunlarla birlikte ortaya &ccedil;Ä±kan psikolojik etkileri de d&uuml;zeltmeyi ama&ccedil;layan bir operasyondur.&nbsp; Bu operasyon Rinoplasti ameliyatlarÄ±na oranla daha zordur. Hasta beklentisinin y&uuml;ksek olduÄŸu ancak buna karÅŸÄ±n baÅŸarÄ± oranÄ±nÄ±n ilk ameliyata g&ouml;re daha d&uuml;ÅŸ&uuml;k olabileceÄŸi bir cerrahidir. AyrÄ±ca hassas bir cerrahi birikim gerektiren ve titizlikle yapÄ±lmasÄ± gereken bir ameliyattÄ±r.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOperasyon, daha &ouml;nce ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸmiÅŸ ameliyat sonrasÄ± ortaya &ccedil;Ä±kan sorunlarÄ±n tedavisi amacÄ±yla uygulanÄ±r.&nbsp; Burnun yeniden ÅŸekillendirilmesi ve y&uuml;zle uyumlu estetik bir g&ouml;r&uuml;n&uuml;m&uuml;n saÄŸlamasÄ± hedeflenir.&nbsp;Burun sÄ±rtÄ±ndaki &ccedil;&ouml;kme (semer burun deformitesi), burun sÄ±rtÄ±ndaki kemer g&ouml;r&uuml;n&uuml;m&uuml;, septum deviasyonu (kemik eÄŸikliÄŸinin), burun i&ccedil;indeki veya dÄ±ÅŸÄ±ndaki doku kaybÄ±ndaki artÄ±ÅŸ, burun etlerinde ÅŸiÅŸlik ve bunlara baÄŸlÄ± nefes alma ÅŸikayetlerinin ortadan kaldÄ±rÄ±lmasÄ±nÄ± ama&ccedil;lar.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOperasyon yaklaÅŸÄ±k 2,5-3 saat s&uuml;rmektedir. Hastalar ameliyattan sonra 1 gece hastanede misafir edilir. Bu s&uuml;re&ccedil;te iyileÅŸmeyi hÄ±zlandÄ±rÄ±cÄ± tedaviler ve soÄŸuk uygulamalarÄ± yapÄ±lÄ±r. KÄ±kÄ±rdak ve kemikler gibi hassas b&ouml;lgeleri korumak adÄ±na al&ccedil;Ä± ve ortasÄ± delik olan bir silikon tampon konulur. Silikon tamponlar 2 g&uuml;n sonra, burun ucu dikiÅŸleri 7 g&uuml;n sonra alÄ±nÄ±r ve hasta g&uuml;nl&uuml;k yaÅŸamÄ±na d&ouml;ner.</p>\r\n','','Revision Rhinoplasty','revision-rhinoplasty',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Revision Rhinoplasty is an operation that has been operated before, but still has nasal deformities and breathing problems, and aims to correct the psychological effects that occur with these problems. This operation is more difficult than Rhinoplasty operations. It is a surgery in which patient expectation is high, but the success rate may be lower than the first surgery. In addition, it is an operation that requires a sensitive surgical experience and must be performed meticulously.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The operation is applied for the treatment of problems that occur after the previous operation. It is aimed to reshape the nose and provide an aesthetic appearance compatible with the face. It aims to eliminate the collapse of the nasal dorsum (saddle nose deformity), the appearance of the arch on the nasal dorsum, the deviation of the septum (bone curvature), the increase in tissue loss inside or outside the nose, the swelling of the nasal concha and the related breathing complaints.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The operation takes approximately 2.5-3 hours. Patients are hosted in the hospital for 1 night after the operation. In this process, treatments that accelerate healing and cold applications are made. In order to protect sensitive areas such as cartilage and bones, a plaster and a silicone pad with a hole in the middle are placed. Silicone pads are removed after 2 days, nasal tip sutures are removed after 7 days and the patient returns to his daily life.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ù…Ø±Ø§Ø¬Ø¹Ø© ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù','content-1770827144-3319',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ù…Ø±Ø§Ø¬Ø¹Ø© Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ù‡ÙŠ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø£Ø¬Ø±ÙŠØª Ù…Ù† Ù‚Ø¨Ù„ ØŒ ÙˆÙ„ÙƒÙ† Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„ØªÙ†ÙØ³ Ù…Ø¹ ØªØ´ÙˆÙ‡Ø§Øª ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ù„Ø§ ØªØ²Ø§Ù„ Ù‚Ø§Ø¦Ù…Ø© ØŒ ÙˆØªÙ‡Ø¯Ù Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ ØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ø¢Ø«Ø§Ø± Ø§Ù„Ù†ÙØ³ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ­Ø¯Ø« Ù…Ø¹ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„. Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø± ØµØ¹ÙˆØ¨Ø© Ù…Ù† Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù. Ø¥Ù†Ù‡Ø§ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ© ÙŠÙƒÙˆÙ† ÙÙŠÙ‡Ø§ ØªÙˆÙ‚Ø¹ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ù…Ø±ØªÙØ¹Ø§ ÙˆÙ„ÙƒÙ† Ù…Ø¹Ø¯Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ù†Ø¬Ø§Ø­ Ù‚Ø¯ ÙŠÙƒÙˆÙ† Ø£Ù‚Ù„ Ù…Ù‚Ø§Ø±Ù†Ø© Ø¨Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø£ÙˆÙ„Ù‰. ÙˆÙ‡ÙŠ Ø£ÙŠØ¶Ø§ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªØªØ·Ù„Ø¨ ØªØ±Ø§ÙƒÙ…Ø§ Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ§ Ø¯Ù‚ÙŠÙ‚Ø§ ÙŠØ¬Ø¨ Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¤Ù‡Ø§ Ø¨Ø¯Ù‚Ø©.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ÙŠØªÙ… ØªÙ†ÙÙŠØ° Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ù„ØºØ±Ø¶ Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ Ù†Ø´Ø£Øª Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø³Ø§Ø¨Ù‚Ø©. ÙŠÙ‡Ø¯Ù Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø¥Ø¹Ø§Ø¯Ø© ØªØ´ÙƒÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ÙˆØªÙˆÙÙŠØ± Ù…Ø¸Ù‡Ø± Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠ Ù…ØªÙˆØ§ÙÙ‚ Ù…Ø¹ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡. ÙˆÙŠÙ‡Ø¯Ù Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ù‚Ø¶Ø§Ø¡ Ø¹Ù„Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ø´ÙƒØ§ÙˆÙ‰ Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù†Ù‡ÙŠØ§Ø± ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø²Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø®Ù„ÙÙŠ Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù (ØªØ´ÙˆÙ‡ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø³ÙŠÙ…Ø±) ØŒ ÙˆØ¸Ù‡ÙˆØ± Ù‚ÙˆØ³ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø²Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø®Ù„ÙÙŠ Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ØŒ ÙˆØ§Ù†Ø­Ø±Ø§Ù Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² (Ø§Ù†Ø­Ù†Ø§Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù…) ØŒ ÙˆØ²ÙŠØ§Ø¯Ø© ÙÙ‚Ø¯Ø§Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ø³Ø¬Ø© Ø¯Ø§Ø®Ù„ Ø£Ùˆ Ø®Ø§Ø±Ø¬ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ØŒ ÙˆØªÙˆØ±Ù… ÙÙŠ Ù„Ø­Ù… Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ØŒ ÙˆÙ…Ø§ ÙŠØ±ØªØ¨Ø· Ø¨Ù‡Ø§ Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„ØªÙ†ÙØ³.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØ³ØªØºØ±Ù‚ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø­ÙˆØ§Ù„ÙŠ Ø³Ø§Ø¹ØªÙŠÙ† ÙˆÙ†ØµÙ Ø£Ùˆ Ø«Ù„Ø§Ø« Ø³Ø§Ø¹Ø§Øª. ÙŠØªÙ… Ø§Ø³ØªØ¶Ø§ÙØ© Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±Ø¶Ù‰ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³ØªØ´ÙÙ‰ Ù„Ù…Ø¯Ø© Ù„ÙŠÙ„Ø© ÙˆØ§Ø­Ø¯Ø© Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ©. ÙÙŠ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØŒ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬Ø§Øª ÙˆØ§Ù„ØªØ·Ø¨ÙŠÙ‚Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø§Ø±Ø¯Ø© Ù„ØªØ³Ø±ÙŠØ¹ Ø§Ù„Ø´ÙØ§Ø¡. Ù…Ù† Ø£Ø¬Ù„ Ø­Ù…Ø§ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù†Ø§Ø·Ù‚ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø³Ø§Ø³Ø© Ù…Ø«Ù„ Ø§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø±ÙˆÙ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… ØŒ&nbsp; ÙŠØªÙ… ÙˆØ¶Ø¹ Ø¬Ø¨ÙŠØ±Ø© Ùˆ ÙˆØ­Ø´Ø§ Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø³ÙŠÙ„ÙŠÙƒÙˆÙ† Ù…Ø¹ ÙˆØ¬ÙˆØ¯ Ø«Ù‚Ø¨ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù†ØªØµÙ. ØªØªÙ… Ø¥Ø²Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø­ÙØ§Ø¦Ø¸ Ø§Ù„Ø³ÙŠÙ„ÙŠÙƒÙˆÙ† Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ ÙŠÙˆÙ…ÙŠÙ† ØŒ ÙˆÙŠØªÙ… Ø¥Ø²Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø®ÙŠÙˆØ· Ø·Ø±Ù Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø³Ø¨Ø¹Ø© Ø£ÙŠØ§Ù… ØŒ ÙˆÙŠØ¹ÙˆØ¯ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø­ÙŠØ§ØªÙ‡ Ø§Ù„ÙŠÙˆÙ…ÙŠØ©.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Revision Rhinoplastik','revision-rhinoplastik',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Revision Rhinoplastik ist eine Operation, die zuvor operiert wurde, aber die Deformit&auml;ten der Nase und Atemprobleme bestehen und darauf abzielt, die psychologischen Effekte zu korrigieren, die mit diesen Problemen auftreten. Diese Operation ist schwieriger als Rhinoplastik-Operationen. Es ist eine Operation, bei der die Erwartungen des Patienten hoch sind, aber die Erfolgsrate niedriger sein kann als bei der ersten Operation. Es ist auch eine Operation, die eine pr&auml;zise chirurgische Akkumulation erfordert und sorgf&auml;ltig durchgef&uuml;hrt werden muss.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDie Operation wird durchgef&uuml;hrt, um Probleme zu behandeln, die nach der Operation aufgetreten sind. Es zielt darauf ab, die Nase neu zu gestalten und ein &auml;sthetisches Aussehen zu bieten, das mit dem Gesicht kompatibel ist. Es zielt darauf ab, den Kollaps des Nasenr&uuml;ckens (Sattelnasendeformit&auml;t), das Auftreten von B&ouml;gen im Nasenr&uuml;cken, die Abweichung des Septums (Knochenneigung), den Anstieg des Gewebeverlustes innerhalb oder au&szlig;erhalb der Nase, Schwellungen des Nasenfleisches und damit verbundene Atembeschwerden zu beseitigen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDie Operation dauert ca. 2,5-3 Stunden. Patienten werden 1 Nacht nach der Operation im Krankenhaus untergebracht. In diesem Prozess werden Behandlungen und kalte Anwendungen durchgef&uuml;hrt, die die Heilung beschleunigen. Um empfindliche Bereiche wie Knorpel und Knochen zu sch&uuml;tzen, werden Gips und ein Silikonpuffer mit einem Loch in der Mitte eingesetzt. Silikonpuffer werden nach 2 Tagen entfernt, Nasen-Stiche nach 7 Tagen und der Patient kehrt in seinen Alltag zur&uuml;ck.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'f702d59a3bb376153fac20220320eyalcin953400e5f4c7d9d00ebc',1,'2022-03-20 17:48:44',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(20,42,'2022-03-20',NULL,'Ä°ple YÃ¼z Germe (FransÄ±z AskÄ±)',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Son d&ouml;nemlerde olduk&ccedil;a pop&uuml;lerleÅŸen bu iÅŸlem, cerrahi operasyonlarÄ± tercih etmeyen hastalar tarafÄ±ndan olduk&ccedil;a ilgi g&ouml;ren bir operasyondur. Y&uuml;z hatlarÄ±ndan memnun olmayan, cilt y&uuml;zeyinde sarkma ve kÄ±rÄ±ÅŸma meydana gelmiÅŸ kiÅŸilerde kullanÄ±lan bu y&ouml;ntem, kÄ±smi y&uuml;z felci ge&ccedil;iren hastalarda da kullanÄ±labilen tedavi edici bir y&ouml;ntemdir. KullanÄ±lan &uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml;n biyolojik anlamda insan v&uuml;cuduna uyumlu olmasÄ± sebebi ile &uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml;n markasÄ±na baÄŸlÄ± olarak yÄ±llarca cilt altÄ±nda kalmasÄ± m&uuml;mk&uuml;nd&uuml;r.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cerrahi operasyonlarÄ±n uzun s&uuml;ren iyileÅŸme s&uuml;re&ccedil;leri ve maliyetleri g&ouml;z &ouml;n&uuml;ne alÄ±ndÄ±ÄŸÄ±nda FransÄ±z askÄ± olduk&ccedil;a konforlu bir tedavi y&ouml;ntemidir. Bu iÅŸlemde y&uuml;z germe ameliyatlarÄ±nda kullanÄ±lan medikal iplikler kullanÄ±lÄ±r. Bu iplerin &uuml;zerinde dokuya tutunmayÄ± saÄŸlayan kÄ±l&ccedil;Ä±klar yer almaktadÄ±r. Operasyon sonrasÄ±nda y&uuml;zdeki kÄ±rÄ±ÅŸÄ±klÄ±klar ve sarkmalarÄ±n tedavisi ama&ccedil;lanÄ±r.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FransÄ±z askÄ± uygulamasÄ±nÄ±n cerrahi operasyonlarla tek farkÄ± kalÄ±cÄ±lÄ±k s&uuml;residir. Ä°ÅŸlem s&uuml;resi ortalama 45 dk ile 1 saat arasÄ±ndadÄ±r. Operasyon sonrasÄ±nda az da olsa &ouml;dem ve iÄŸne izi kalabilir. &nbsp;Bu ÅŸikayetler ortalama 1 hafta s&uuml;rer sonrasÄ±nda g&uuml;nl&uuml;k hayatÄ±nÄ±za devam edebilirsiniz. HÄ±zlÄ± hareketler ve &ccedil;ene hareketleri sÄ±rasÄ±nda iplerin bulunduÄŸu yerlerde gerginlik hissedilebilir. Bu ÅŸikayetlerde genellikle 2. haftadan sonra kaybolur.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ä°ÅŸlemden sonra 1 ay s&uuml;re ile y&uuml;z&uuml;st&uuml; yatÄ±lmasÄ±, kabuklu ve sert yiyeceklerin yenilmesi, abartÄ±lÄ± mimik hareketi yapÄ±lmasÄ±, &ccedil;enenin &ccedil;ok fazla a&ccedil;Ä±lmasÄ±nÄ± gerektiren hareketler &ouml;nerilmemektedir.</p>\r\n','','Thread Face Lift (French Strap)',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p>This procedure, which has become very popular recently, is an operation that attracts a lot of attention by patients who do not prefer surgical operations. This method, which is used in people who are not satisfied with their facial features, and who have sagging and wrinkling on the skin surface, is a therapeutic method that can also be used in patients with partial facial paralysis. Since the product used is biologically compatible with the human body, it is possible to remain under the skin for years depending on the brand of the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Considering the long healing processes and costs of surgical operations, the French sling is a very comfortable treatment method. In this process, medical threads used in face lift surgeries are used. There are awns on these threads that provide attachment to the tissue. After the operation, it is aimed to treat the wrinkles and sagging on the face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The only difference between the French sling and surgical operations is the permanence period. The processing time is between 45 minutes and 1 hour on average. After the operation, a little edema and needle scar may remain. These complaints last for an average of 1 week, then you can continue with your daily life. During fast movements and jaw movements, tension may be felt in the places where the ropes are located. These complaints usually disappear after the 2nd week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the procedure, it is not recommended to lie face down for 1 month, eat crusty and hard foods, make exaggerated mimic movements, and movements that require the jaw to be opened too much.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ø´Ø¯ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ Ø¨Ø­Ø¨Ù„ (Ø­Ø²Ø§Ù… ÙØ±Ù†Ø³ÙŠ )',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ù‡Ø°Ø§ Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ ØŒ Ø§Ù„Ø°ÙŠ Ø£ØµØ¨Ø­ Ø´Ø§Ø¦Ø¹Ø§ Ø¬Ø¯Ø§ Ù…Ø¤Ø®Ø±Ø§ØŒ Ù‡Ùˆ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªØ­Ø¸Ù‰ Ø¨Ø´Ø¹Ø¨ÙŠØ© ÙƒØ¨ÙŠØ±Ø© Ù„Ø¯Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±Ø¶Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ø°ÙŠÙ