Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ ØŒ ÙÙ…Ù† ØºÙŠØ± Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³ØªØ­Ø³Ù† Ø£Ù† ÙŠÙƒØ°Ø¨ ÙˆØ¬Ù‡Ù‡ Ù„Ø£Ø³ÙÙ„ Ù„Ù…Ø¯Ø© Ø´Ù‡Ø±Ø§ ØŒ ÙˆØªÙ†Ø§ÙˆÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø·Ø¹Ù…Ø© Ø§Ù„Ù‚Ø´Ø±Ø© ÙˆØ§Ù„ØµÙ„Ø¨Ø© ØŒ ÙˆØ¬Ø¹Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø±ÙƒØ§Øª ØªÙ‚Ù„ÙŠØ¯ Ù…Ø¨Ø§Ù„Øº ÙÙŠÙ‡Ø§ ØŒ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø­Ø±ÙƒØ§Øª Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØªØ·Ù„Ø¨ Ø§Ù„ÙƒØ«ÙŠØ± Ù…Ù† ÙØªØ­ Ø§Ù„ÙÙƒ.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Facelift mit Faden (FranzoÌˆsischer Riemen)',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Dieses Verfahren, das in letzter Zeit sehr populaÌˆr geworden ist, ist eine Operation, die viel Aufmerksamkeit von Patienten auf sich zieht, die chirurgische Eingriffe nicht bevorzugen. Diese Methode, die bei Menschen angewendet wird, die mit ihren GesichtszuÌˆgen unzufrieden sind und die eine Erschlaffung und Faltenbildung auf der HautoberflaÌˆche haben, ist eine therapeutische Methode, die auch bei Patienten mit partieller GesichtslaÌˆhmung angewendet werden kann. Da das verwendete Produkt mit dem menschlichen KoÌˆrper biologisch vertraÌˆglich ist, ist es je nach Produktmarke moÌˆglich, jahrelang unter der Haut zu bleiben.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Anbetracht der langen Heilungsprozesse und Kosten chirurgischer Eingriffe ist die franzoÌˆsische Schlinge eine sehr komfortable Behandlungsmethode. Bei diesem Verfahren</p>\r\n\r\n<p>werden medizinische FaÌˆden verwendet, die bei Facelift-Operationen verwendet werden. Auf diesen FaÌˆden befinden sich Grannen, die eine Befestigung am Gewebe ermoÌˆglichen. Nach der Operation sollen die Falten und die Erschlaffung des Gesichts behandelt werden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der einzige Unterschied zwischen der franzoÌˆsischen Schlinge und chirurgischen Eingriffen ist die Verweildauer. Die Bearbeitungszeit betraÌˆgt durchschnittlich zwischen 45 Minuten und 1 Stunde. Nach der Operation kann ein kleines OÌˆdem und eine Nadelnarbe zuruÌˆckbleiben. Diese Beschwerden halten durchschnittlich 1 Woche an, danach koÌˆnnen Sie Ihr taÌˆgliches Leben fortsetzen. Bei schnellen Bewegungen und Kieferbewegungen kann an den Stellen, an denen sich die Seile befinden, eine Spannung zu spuÌˆren sein. Diese Beschwerden verschwinden in der Regel nach der 2. Woche.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nach dem Eingriff wird davon abgeraten, 1 Monat lang mit dem Gesicht nach unten zu liegen, knusprige und harte Speisen zu sich zu nehmen, uÌˆbertriebene mimische Bewegungen auszufuÌˆhren und Bewegungen auszufuÌˆhren, bei denen der Kiefer zu weit geoÌˆffnet werden muss.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'02954f0720e18e0a7ff720220320eyalcin7c3c20a2dd49dcaa1cb1',1,'2022-03-20 17:49:48',NULL,NULL,NULL,-1),(21,43,'2022-03-20',NULL,'Badem GÃ¶z EstetiÄŸi','badem-gz-estetii',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Badem g&ouml;z estetiÄŸi tamamen estetik ama&ccedil;la ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirilir. Bu operasyon ile g&ouml;z&uuml;n dÄ±ÅŸ kenarÄ± yukarÄ±ya &ccedil;ekilerek daha &ccedil;ekik g&ouml;r&uuml;nmesi ama&ccedil;lanÄ±r. Burada dikkat edilmesi gereken en &ouml;nemli husus &ccedil;ekikliÄŸin g&ouml;ze uygun olmasÄ±dÄ±r. Genel ama&ccedil; makyajla verilmeye &ccedil;alÄ±ÅŸÄ±lan g&ouml;r&uuml;nt&uuml;n&uuml;n kalÄ±cÄ± hale getirilmesidir.&nbsp;SanÄ±lanÄ±n aksine badem g&ouml;z estetiÄŸinde g&ouml;zler b&uuml;y&uuml;mez, sadece daha &ccedil;ekik hale gelir.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOperasyon ortalama 1 saat s&uuml;rmektedir. Kombine cerrahi&nbsp; yapÄ±lÄ±p yapÄ±lmamasÄ±na g&ouml;re hastanede kalÄ±ÅŸ s&uuml;resi deÄŸiÅŸebilir. Sadece badem g&ouml;z estetiÄŸi olan hasta aynÄ± g&uuml;n taburcu edilir. Genellikle 5-7 g&uuml;n arasÄ±nda dikiÅŸler alÄ±nÄ±r, bu s&uuml;re sonunda y&uuml;zdeki &ouml;demler &ouml;nemli oranda azalÄ±r ve hasta normal hayatÄ±na d&ouml;n&uuml;ÅŸ yapabilir.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','Almond Eye Aesthetics','almond-eye-aesthetics',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Almond eye aesthetics is performed for purely aesthetic purposes. With this operation, it is aimed to make the outer edge of the eye look more slanted by pulling up. The most important thing to note here is that the slanting is suitable for the eye. The general purpose is to make the image that is tried to be given with make-up permanent. Contrary to popular belief, the eyes do not grow in almond eye aesthetics, they just become more slanting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The operation takes an average of 1 hour. Depending on whether or not combined surgery is performed, the length of stay in the hospital may vary. The patient with only almond eye aesthetics is discharged on the same day. Generally, the stitches are removed between 5-7 days, after which the edema on the face decreases significantly and the patient can return to his normal life.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø¹ÙŠÙ† Ø§Ù„Ù„ÙˆØ²','content-1770827144-1304',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">ÙŠØªÙ… Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø¹ÙŠÙ† Ø§Ù„Ù„ÙˆØ² Ù„Ø£ØºØ±Ø§Ø¶ Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø¨Ø­ØªØ©. ÙÙŠ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØŒ ÙŠØªÙ… Ø³Ø­Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§ÙØ© Ø§Ù„Ø®Ø§Ø±Ø¬ÙŠØ© Ù„Ù„Ø¹ÙŠÙ† Ø¨Ø­ÙŠØ« ØªØ¨Ø¯Ùˆ Ù…Ø§Ø¦Ù„Ø© Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø±. Ø£Ù‡Ù… Ø´ÙŠØ¡ ÙŠØ¬Ø¨ Ù…Ù„Ø§Ø­Ø¸ØªÙ‡ Ù‡Ù†Ø§ Ù‡Ùˆ Ø£Ù† Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ù…Ù†Ø§Ø³Ø¨ Ù„Ù„Ø¹ÙŠÙ†. Ø§Ù„ØºØ±Ø¶ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø§Ù… Ù‡Ùˆ Ø¬Ø¹Ù„ Ø§Ù„ØµÙˆØ±Ø© Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ÙŠÙØ­Ø§ÙˆÙ„ ØªÙ‚Ø¯ÙŠÙ…Ù‡Ø§ Ø¨Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙƒÙŠØ§Ø¬ Ø¯Ø§Ø¦Ù…Ø©. Ø®Ù„Ø§ÙØ§ Ù„Ù„Ø§Ø¹ØªÙ‚Ø§Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø´Ø§Ø¦Ø¹ ØŒ Ù„Ø§ ØªÙ†Ù…Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ø¹ÙŠÙˆÙ† ÙÙŠ Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø¹ÙŠÙ† Ø§Ù„Ù„ÙˆØ² ØŒ Ø¨Ù„ ØªØµØ¨Ø­ Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø± Ù…ÙŠÙ„Ù‹Ø§.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØ³ØªØºØ±Ù‚ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…ØªÙˆØ³Ø· Ù¡ Ø³Ø§Ø¹Ø©. Ø§Ø¹ØªÙ…Ø§Ø¯Ø§ Ø¹Ù„Ù‰ Ù…Ø§ Ø¥Ø°Ø§ ØªÙ… Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ© Ù…Ø´ØªØ±ÙƒØ© ØŒ Ù‚Ø¯ ØªØ®ØªÙ„Ù Ù…Ø¯Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ù‚Ø§Ù…Ø© ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³ØªØ´ÙÙ‰. ÙŠØªÙ… ØªÙØ±ÙŠØº Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ø§Ù„Ø°ÙŠ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ù…Ù† Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø¹ÙŠÙ† Ø§Ù„Ù„ÙˆØ² ÙÙ‚Ø· ÙÙŠ Ù†ÙØ³ Ø§Ù„ÙŠÙˆÙ…. Ø¹Ø§Ø¯Ø© ØŒ ØªØ¤Ø®Ø° ØºØ±Ø² Ø¨ÙŠÙ†Ù¥ Ùˆ Ù§ Ø£ÙŠØ§Ù… ØŒ ÙˆØ¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø°Ù„Ùƒ Ø§Ù„ÙˆÙ‚Øª ÙˆØ°Ù…Ø© Ø¹Ù„Ù‰ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ Ø®ÙØ¶Øª Ø¨Ø´ÙƒÙ„ ÙƒØ¨ÙŠØ± ÙˆÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† Ù„Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ø§Ù„Ø¹ÙˆØ¯Ø© Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø­ÙŠØ§ØªÙ‡ Ø§Ù„Ø·Ø¨ÙŠØ¹ÙŠØ©.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Mandelaugen-Ã„sthetik','mandelaugen-sthetik',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Mandel Augen&auml;sthetik wird zu rein &auml;sthetischen Zwecken durchgef&uuml;hrt. Mit dieser Operation soll der &auml;u&szlig;ere Rand des Auges nach oben gezogen werden, um schr&auml;ger auszusehen. Das Wichtigste, was hier zu beachten ist, ist, dass die schr&auml;ge nicht f&uuml;r das Auge geeignet ist. Das allgemeine Ziel ist es, das Bild, das mit Make-up versucht wird, dauerhaft zu machen. Entgegen der landl&auml;ufigen Meinung wachsen die Mandelaugen nicht, sie werden nur schr&auml;ger.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Operation dauert durchschnittlich 1 Stunde. Je nachdem, ob eine kombinierte Operation durchgef&uuml;hrt wird oder nicht, kann sich die Dauer des Krankenhausaufenthalts &auml;ndern. Nur Patienten mit Mandelaugen werden am selben Tag entlassen. In der Regel werden die Stiche zwischen 5-7 Tagen entfernt, nach dieser Zeit werden die &Ouml;deme im Gesicht deutlich reduziert und der Patient kann in sein normales Leben zur&uuml;ckkehren.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'57b94f48f6172d25f52b20220320eyalcin858b89de9e5062ebe328',1,'2022-03-20 17:50:24',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(22,8,'2022-03-21',NULL,'YÃ¼z ProsedÃ¼rleri','yz-prosedrleri',1,NULL,NULL,'','','Facial Procedures',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Enhance the beauty of your face with our tailored procedures.','','Процедуры для лица',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Подчеркните красоту вашего лица с нашими процедурами.','','إجراءات الوجه',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'تعزيز جمال وجهك باستخدام إجراءاتنا المخصصة.','','Procédures faciales',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Mettez en valeur la beauté de votre visage grâce à nos procédures.','','Gesichtsbehandlungen',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Unterstreichen Sie die Schönheit Ihres Gesichts mit unseren Behandlungen.','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'7153a38555462c248cae20220321eyalcin7bb02bfdaa8d55a54386',1,'2022-03-21 10:28:47',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(23,8,'2022-03-21',NULL,'AmeliyatsÄ±z Ä°ÅŸlemler','ameliyatsz-lemler',1,NULL,NULL,'','','Non-Surgical Procedures',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Rejuvenate your skin without surgical intervention.','','Безоперационные процедуры',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Омолодите свою кожу без хирургического вмешательства.','','الإجراءات غير الجراحية',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'تجديد شباب بشرتك دون تدخل جراحي.','','Procédures non chirurgicales',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Rajeunissez votre peau sans intervention chirurgicale.','','Nicht-chirurgische Eingriffe',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'Verjüngen Sie Ihre Haut ohne chirurgischen Eingriff.','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'d98c220a587ab416b0b920220321eyalcin7b6db737fd3e48fc5e74',1,'2022-03-21 10:29:29',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(24,46,'2022-03-21',NULL,'Neden EstetiÄŸi Tercih Ettiniz ?','neden-estetii-tercih-ettiniz',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>BaktÄ±ÄŸÄ±m her ÅŸeyde hekim olarak bir g&uuml;zellik arÄ±yorum. Buna doÄŸa, insan, hayvan ve bitki dahil. Sinema, televizyon ve resim gibi kiÅŸisel sanatlara da ilgi duyuyorum.</p>\r\n','','Why Did You Prefer Aesthetics?','why-did-you-prefer-aesthetics',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>As a doctor, I look for beauty in everything I look at. This includes nature, humans, animals and plants. I am also interested in personal arts such as cinema, television and painting.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ù„Ù…Ø§Ø°Ø§ Ø§Ø®ØªØ±Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§ØªØŸ','content-1770827144-8046',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø£Ù†Ø§ Ø£Ø¨Ø­Ø« Ø¹Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ ÙƒØ·Ø¨ÙŠØ¨ ÙÙŠ ÙƒÙ„ Ù…Ø§ Ù†Ù†Ø¸Ø±. ÙˆÙ‡Ø°Ø§ ÙŠØ´Ù…Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ø·Ø¨ÙŠØ¹Ø© ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¥Ù†Ø³Ø§Ù† ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø­ÙŠÙˆØ§Ù†Ø§Øª ÙˆØ§Ù„Ù†Ø¨Ø§ØªØ§Øª. Ø£Ù†Ø§ Ù…Ù‡ØªÙ… Ø£ÙŠØ¶Ø§ Ø¨Ø§Ù„ÙÙ†ÙˆÙ† Ø§Ù„Ø´Ø®ØµÙŠØ© Ù…Ø«Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ø³ÙŠÙ†Ù…Ø§ ÙˆØ§Ù„ØªÙ„ÙØ²ÙŠÙˆÙ† ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø±Ø³Ù….&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Warum haben Sie Ã„sthetik bevorzugt?','warum-haben-sie-sthetik-bevorzugt',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Als Arzt achte ich bei allem, was ich betrachte, auf Sch&ouml;nheit. Dazu geh&ouml;ren Natur, Menschen, Tiere und Pflanzen. Ich interessiere mich auch f&uuml;r pers&ouml;nliche K&uuml;nste wie Kino, TV und Malerei.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'e49b8fe3bd029ba5725a20220321eyalcin274ed8e2e22c831ff177',1,'2022-03-21 11:10:35',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(25,46,'2022-03-21',NULL,'Estetik operasyonlar psikolojiyi nasÄ±l etkiliyor ?','estetik-operasyonlar-psikolojiyi-nasl-etkiliyor',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Estetik operasyonlar psikolojik etkileri olduk&ccedil;a g&uuml;&ccedil;l&uuml; olan iÅŸlemlerdir. Benim hastalarÄ±mda en &ccedil;ok g&ouml;zlemlediÄŸim nokta &ouml;zg&uuml;ven artÄ±ÅŸÄ±. KÄ±sacasÄ± estetik operasyonlarÄ±n pozitif etkilerini&nbsp;sÄ±k&ccedil;a tecr&uuml;be ediyorum.</p>\r\n','','How does plastic surgery affect psychology?','how-does-plastic-surgery-affect-psychology',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Aesthetic operations are procedures with very strong psychological effects. The point I have observed most in my patients is the increase in self-confidence. In short, I frequently experience the positive effects of aesthetic operations.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','ÙƒÙŠÙ ØªØ¤Ø«Ø± Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø¹Ù„Ù‰ Ø¹Ù„Ù… Ø§Ù„Ù†ÙØ³ØŸ','content-1770827144-7823',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ© Ù‡ÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªÙƒÙˆÙ† Ø¢Ø«Ø§Ø±Ù‡Ø§ Ø§Ù„Ù†ÙØ³ÙŠØ© Ù‚ÙˆÙŠØ© Ø¬Ø¯Ø§. Ø§Ù„Ù†Ù‚Ø·Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø± Ø´ÙŠÙˆØ¹Ø§ Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ Ø£Ù„Ø§Ø­Ø¸Ù‡Ø§ ÙÙŠ Ù…Ø±Ø¶Ø§ÙŠ Ù‡ÙŠ Ø²ÙŠØ§Ø¯Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø«Ù‚Ø© Ø¨Ø§Ù„Ù†ÙØ³. Ø¨Ø§Ø®ØªØµØ§Ø± ØŒ ØºØ§Ù„Ø¨Ø§ Ù…Ø§ Ø£Ø¬Ø±Ù‘Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø¢Ø«Ø§Ø± Ø§Ù„Ø¥ÙŠØ¬Ø§Ø¨ÙŠØ© Ù„Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ©.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Wie wirkt sich plastische Chirurgie auf die Psychologie aus?','wie-wirkt-sich-plastische-chirurgie-auf-die-psychologie-aus',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>&Auml;sthetische Operationen sind Eingriffe mit sehr starker psychologischer Wirkung. Was ich bei meinen Patienten am meisten beobachte, ist die Steigerung des Selbstbewusstseins. Kurz gesagt erlebe ich h&auml;ufig die positive Wirkung &auml;sthetischer Operationen.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'8ec1ec611ca40fe3fdd720220321eyalcin7ddafe240a51f7c754d2',1,'2022-03-21 11:10:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(26,46,'2022-03-21',NULL,'Ä°ÅŸlemim nerede yapÄ±lacak?','lemim-nerede-yaplacak',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Cerrahi gerektirmeyen iÅŸlemleri kendi kliniÄŸimde yapÄ±yorum. AmeliyatlarÄ± ise &ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;m ortaklÄ±ÄŸÄ± yaptÄ±ÄŸÄ±mÄ±z &Ouml;zel Hastanelerde ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtiriyorum.</p>\r\n','','Where will my procedure be done?','where-will-my-procedure-be-done',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>I do non-surgical procedures in my own clinic. I perform the surgeries in Private Hospitals with which we are solution partners.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ø£ÙŠÙ† Ø³ÙŠØªÙ… ØªÙ†ÙÙŠØ° Ù…Ø¹Ø§Ù…Ù„ØªÙŠØŸ','content-1770827144-5581',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø£Ù‚ÙˆÙ… Ø¨Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ù„Ø§ ØªØªØ·Ù„Ø¨ Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© ÙÙŠ Ø¹ÙŠØ§Ø¯ØªÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø®Ø§ØµØ©. Ø£Ù‚ÙˆÙ… Ø¨Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ© ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³ØªØ´ÙÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø®Ø§ØµØ© Ø­ÙŠØ« Ù†Ø­Ù† Ø´Ø±ÙŠÙƒ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ù„.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Wo wird mein Eingriff durchgefÃ¼hrt?','wo-wird-mein-eingriff-durchgefhrt',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Ich f&uuml;hre nicht-chirurgische Eingriffe in meiner eigenen Klinik durch. Operationen, die eine chirurgische Eingriffe erfordern, f&uuml;hre ich in Privatkliniken durch, mit denen wir L&ouml;sungspartner sind.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'23b56b04ca2bb6fe3efc20220321eyalcin9b3f0fdd629c977554a5',1,'2022-03-21 11:11:17',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(27,46,'2022-03-21',NULL,'Ameliyat SÃ¼reci NasÄ±l Ä°ÅŸliyor ?','ameliyat-sreci-nasl-liyor',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>&Ouml;ncelikle muayene olmaya geliyorsunuz. Daha sonrasÄ±nda yapÄ±lacak iÅŸlemleri konuÅŸuyoruz. Daha sonrasÄ±nda da ameliyata karar veriyoruz. Ameliyat sonrasÄ± 5. g&uuml;n dikiÅŸ alma iÅŸlemleri ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸiyor. Ä°yileÅŸme s&uuml;reci de ortalama 7-10 g&uuml;n kadar s&uuml;r&uuml;yor.</p>\r\n','','How Does the Surgery Process Work?','how-does-the-surgery-process-work',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>First of all, you come to be examined. We talk about what to do next. Then we decide on the surgery. Stitches are removed on the 5th day after the surgery. The healing process takes about 7-10 days on average.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','ÙƒÙŠÙ ØªØ¹Ù…Ù„ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø©ØŸ','content-1770827144-1966',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø¯Ø§ÙŠØ© ØŒ Ø³ÙˆÙ ØªØ£ØªÙŠ Ù„ÙØ­ØµÙ‡Ø§. ÙÙ†Ø­Ù† Ù†ØªØ­Ø¯Ø« Ø¹Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡Ø§Øª. Ø«Ù… Ù†Ù‚Ø±Ø± Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ© Ù…Ù†Ø§Ø³Ø¨ Ù„Ùƒ. ØªØªÙ… Ø¥Ø²Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø§Ù„ØºØ±Ø² ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„ÙŠÙˆÙ… Ø§Ù„Ø®Ø§Ù…Ø³ Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø©. ØªØ³ØªØºØ±Ù‚ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ø´ÙØ§Ø¡ Ø£ÙŠØ¶Ø§ Ø­ÙˆØ§Ù„ÙŠ Ù§ -Ù¡Ù &nbsp; Ø£ÙŠØ§Ù… ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…ØªÙˆØ³Ø·.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Wie funktioniert der Operationsprozess?','wie-funktioniert-der-operationsprozess',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Zun&auml;chst einmal kommen Sie zur Untersuchung. Wir besprechen, was als n&auml;chstes zu tun ist. Dann entscheiden wir uns f&uuml;r die Operation. Die F&auml;den werden am 5. Tag nach der Operation entfernt. Der Heilungsprozess dauert im Durchschnitt etwa 7-10 Tage.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'5701f0783652fb297da620220321eyalcin4acfef181ea95c30abba',1,'2022-03-21 11:11:37',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(28,5,'2022-03-22',NULL,'Fotogaleri','fotogaleri',1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'c031377fada7c5a64f1d20220322eyalcin432133f2853a4a79a7f9',1,'2022-03-22 15:48:31',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(29,43,'2022-04-07',NULL,'Rinoplasti','rinoplasti',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Rinoplasti burundaki ÅŸekil bozukluklarÄ±nÄ± &ccedil;&ouml;zmeyi ve bu sorunlarla birlikte ortaya &ccedil;Ä±kan psikolojik etkileri de d&uuml;zeltmeyi ama&ccedil;layan bir operasyondur. Bu operasyonda y&uuml;z, bir b&uuml;t&uuml;n olarak deÄŸerlendirilir ve y&uuml;z&uuml;n genel yapÄ±sÄ±na ve ifadesine g&ouml;re en uygun m&uuml;dahale ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirilir. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HastanÄ±n t&uuml;m saÄŸlÄ±k ge&ccedil;miÅŸi de burun problemleriyle birlikte operasyon &ouml;ncesinde b&uuml;t&uuml;n olarak g&ouml;z &ouml;n&uuml;nde bulundurulur. Burunda baÅŸkaca i&ccedil; bozukluÄŸun olup olmadÄ±ÄŸÄ±; hastanÄ±n alerjik durumlarÄ±, daha &ouml;nce ge&ccedil;irdiÄŸi ameliyatlar veya y&uuml;z travmalarÄ± ayrÄ±ntÄ±lÄ± bir bi&ccedil;imde deÄŸerlendirilir. T&uuml;m bu veriler Ä±ÅŸÄ±ÄŸÄ±nda hasta i&ccedil;in en uygun olan y&ouml;ntem se&ccedil;ilir ve uygulanÄ±r. Operasyon a&ccedil;Ä±k ya da kapalÄ± teknikle yapÄ±labilir. EÄŸri olan ve nefes almada soruna neden olan kemik ve kÄ±kÄ±rdaklar &ccedil;Ä±karÄ±lÄ±r, ÅŸekil verilerek tekrar burun i&ccedil;erisine yerleÅŸtirilir. Operasyonda burun i&ccedil;erisindeki kÄ±kÄ±rdak, kemik, bu yapÄ±larÄ± bir arada tutan baÄŸlar ve doku m&uuml;mk&uuml;n olduÄŸunca korunmaya &ccedil;alÄ±ÅŸÄ±lÄ±r. AyrÄ±ca nefes almada tÄ±kanÄ±klÄ±ÄŸa neden olan burun eti b&uuml;y&uuml;mesi ya da kist varsa bu patolojilere de aynÄ± anda m&uuml;dahale edilir. &Ouml;zet olarak rinoplasti hassas bir cerrahi birikim gerektiren ve titizlikle yapÄ±lmasÄ± gereken bir ameliyattÄ±r.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operasyon burnu yeniden ÅŸekillendirmek ve y&uuml;zle uyumlu estetik bir g&ouml;r&uuml;n&uuml;m saÄŸlamak amacÄ±yla uygulanÄ±r. Bu operasyonla burun k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;lt&uuml;lebilir; burnun &uuml;st dudak ile olan a&ccedil;Ä±sÄ± deÄŸiÅŸtirilebilir, burun ucu onarÄ±lÄ±p burundaki girinti, &ccedil;Ä±kÄ±ntÄ± gibi diÄŸer kusurlar d&uuml;zeltilebilir, burnunuza ÅŸeklini veren kemikler ve kÄ±kÄ±rdak &uuml;zerinde d&uuml;zeltme yapÄ±larak septum yapÄ±sÄ± d&uuml;zleÅŸtirilir. Septum, burun deliklerinizi ayÄ±ran kÄ±kÄ±rdak ve kemikten oluÅŸan yapÄ±dÄ±r.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operasyon yaklaÅŸÄ±k 2-3 saat s&uuml;rmektedir. Hastalar ameliyattan sonra 1 gece hastanede misafir edilir. Bu s&uuml;re&ccedil;te iyileÅŸmeyi hÄ±zlandÄ±rÄ±cÄ± tedaviler ve soÄŸuk uygulamalarÄ± yapÄ±lÄ±r. KÄ±kÄ±rdak ve kemikler gibi hassas b&ouml;lgeleri korumak adÄ±na al&ccedil;Ä± veya plastik bir atel ve ortasÄ± delik olan bir silikon tampon konulur. Silikon tamponlar 2 g&uuml;n sonra, burun ucu dikiÅŸleri ise 7 g&uuml;n sonra alÄ±nÄ±r ve hasta g&uuml;nl&uuml;k yaÅŸamÄ±na d&ouml;ner.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','Rhinoplasty','rhinoplasty',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Rhinoplasty is an operation that aims to solve the deformities of the nose and to correct the psychological effects that occur with these problems. In this operation, the face is evaluated as a whole and the most appropriate intervention is performed according to the general structure and expression of the face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The patient&#39;s entire health history, along with nasal problems, is considered as a whole before the operation. Whether there is any other internal disorder in the nose; The patient&#39;s allergic conditions, previous surgeries or facial trauma are evaluated in detail. In the light of all these data, the most appropriate method for the patient is selected and applied. The operation can be performed with open or closed technique. Bone and cartilages that are curved and cause breathing problems are removed, shaped and placed back into the nose. In the operation, the cartilage, bone, ligaments and tissue that hold these structures together in the nose are tried to be preserved as much as possible. In addition, if there is an enlarged nasal cavity or cyst that causes obstruction in breathing, these pathologies are also intervened at the same time. In summary, rhinoplasty is an operation that requires a delicate surgical experience and must be performed meticulously.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The operation is applied to reshape the nose and provide an aesthetic appearance compatible with the face. With this operation, the nose can be reduced; The angle of the nose with the upper lip can be changed, the tip of the nose is repaired and other defects such as indentation and protrusion in the nose can be corrected, the septum structure is straightened by correcting the bones and cartilage that shape your nose. The septum is the cartilage and bone structure that separates your nostrils.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The operation takes about 2-3 hours. Patients are hosted in the hospital for 1 night after the operation. In this process, treatments that accelerate healing and cold applications are made. A plaster or plastic splint and a silicone pad with a hole in the middle are placed to protect sensitive areas such as cartilage and bones. Silicone pads are removed after 2 days and nasal tip sutures are removed after 7 days and the patient returns to his daily life.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù','content-1770827144-4633',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\"><strong>ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ù‡ÙŠ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªÙ‡Ø¯Ù Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø­Ù„ ØªØ´ÙˆÙ‡Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ÙˆØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ø¢Ø«Ø§Ø± Ø§Ù„Ù†ÙØ³ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ­Ø¯Ø« Ù…Ø¹ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„. ÙÙŠ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØŒ ÙŠØªÙ… ØªÙ‚ÙŠÙŠÙ… Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ ÙƒÙƒÙ„ ÙˆÙŠØªÙ… ØªÙ†ÙÙŠØ° Ø§Ù„ØªØ¯Ø®Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ø³Ø¨ ÙˆÙÙ‚Ø§ Ù„Ù„Ù‡ÙŠÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø§Ù… ÙˆØ§Ù„ØªØ¹Ø¨ÙŠØ± Ø¹Ù† Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡. Ø¨Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ø¶Ø§ÙØ© Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ØŒ ÙŠØªÙ… Ø£Ø®Ø° Ø§Ù„ØªØ§Ø±ÙŠØ® Ø§Ù„Ø·Ø¨ÙŠ Ø§Ù„ÙƒØ§Ù…Ù„ Ù„Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ù‚Ø¨Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø§Ø¹ØªØ¨Ø§Ø± ÙƒÙƒÙ„. Ù…Ø§ Ø¥Ø°Ø§ ÙƒØ§Ù†Øª Ù‡Ù†Ø§Ùƒ Ø§Ø¶Ø·Ø±Ø§Ø¨Ø§Øª Ø¯Ø§Ø®Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø£Ø®Ø±Ù‰ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø› ÙŠØªÙ… ØªÙ‚ÙŠÙŠÙ… Ø­Ø§Ù„Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø³Ø§Ø³ÙŠØ© Ù„Ø¯Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ø£Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ø³Ø§Ø¨Ù‚Ø© Ø£Ùˆ ØµØ¯Ù…Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ Ø¨Ø§Ù„ØªÙØµÙŠÙ„. ÙÙŠ Ø¶ÙˆØ¡ ÙƒÙ„ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¨ÙŠØ§Ù†Ø§Øª ØŒ ÙŠØªÙ… Ø§Ø®ØªÙŠØ§Ø± Ø§Ù„Ø·Ø±ÙŠÙ‚Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø± Ù…Ù„Ø§Ø¡Ù…Ø© Ù„Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ ÙˆØªØ·Ø¨ÙŠÙ‚Ù‡Ø§. ÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø¨ØªÙ‚Ù†ÙŠØ© Ù…ÙØªÙˆØ­Ø© Ø£Ùˆ Ù…ØºÙ„Ù‚Ø©. ØªØªÙ… Ø¥Ø²Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… ÙˆØ§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø§Ø±ÙŠÙ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù†Ø­Ù†ÙŠØ© ÙˆØ§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ³Ø¨Ø¨ Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„ØªÙ†ÙØ³ ÙˆØªØ´ÙƒÙŠÙ„Ù‡Ø§ ÙˆÙˆØ¶Ø¹Ù‡Ø§ Ù…Ø±Ø© Ø£Ø®Ø±Ù‰ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù. ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØŒ ØªØªÙ… Ù…Ø­Ø§ÙˆÙ„Ø© Ø­Ù…Ø§ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø±ÙˆÙ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø±ÙˆØ§Ø¨Ø· ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ø³Ø¬Ø© ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ±Ø¨Ø· Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ù‡ÙŠØ§ÙƒÙ„ Ù…Ø¹Ø§ Ù‚Ø¯Ø± Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ù…ÙƒØ§Ù†. Ø¨Ø§Ù„Ø¥Ø¶Ø§ÙØ© Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø°Ù„Ùƒ ØŒ Ø¥Ø°Ø§ ÙƒØ§Ù† Ù‡Ù†Ø§Ùƒ ØªØ¶Ø®Ù… ÙÙŠ Ù„Ø­Ù… Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø£Ùˆ ÙƒÙŠØ³ ÙŠØ³Ø¨Ø¨ Ø§Ø­ØªÙ‚Ø§Ù† ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„ØªÙ†ÙØ³ ØŒ ÙØ¥Ù† Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„ ØªØªØ¯Ø®Ù„ Ø£ÙŠØ¶Ø§. Ø¨Ø§Ø®ØªØµØ§Ø± ØŒ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªØ¬Ù…ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ù‡ÙŠ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªØªØ·Ù„Ø¨ ØªØ±Ø§ÙƒÙ…Ø§ Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠØ§ Ø¯Ù‚ÙŠÙ‚Ø§ ÙˆÙŠØ¬Ø¨ Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¤Ù‡Ø§ Ø¨Ø¯Ù‚Ø©. ÙŠØªÙ… Ø¥Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ù…Ù† Ø£Ø¬Ù„ Ø¥Ø¹Ø§Ø¯Ø© ØªØ´ÙƒÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ÙˆØªÙˆÙÙŠØ± Ù…Ø¸Ù‡Ø± Ø¬Ù…Ø§Ù„ÙŠ Ù…ØªÙˆØ§ÙÙ‚ Ù…Ø¹ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡. Ù…Ø¹ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØŒ ÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† ØªÙ‚Ù„ÙŠÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø› ÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† ØªØºÙŠÙŠØ± Ø²Ø§ÙˆÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ù…Ø¹ Ø§Ù„Ø´ÙØ© Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù„ÙŠØ§ ØŒ ÙˆÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† Ø¥ØµÙ„Ø§Ø­ Ø·Ø±Ù Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ÙˆÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† ØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ø¹ÙŠÙˆØ¨ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø®Ø±Ù‰ Ù…Ø«Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³Ø§ÙØ© Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø§Ø¯Ø¦Ø© ØŒ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¨Ø±ÙˆØ² ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ØŒ ÙˆÙŠØªÙ… ØªØ³Ø·ÙŠØ­ Ø¨Ù†ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø¹Ù† Ø·Ø±ÙŠÙ‚ ØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… ÙˆØ§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø§Ø±ÙŠÙ Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ¹Ø·ÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø´ÙƒÙ„Ù‡. Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ù‡Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ù‡ÙŠÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ø°ÙŠ ÙŠØªÙƒÙˆÙ† Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø±ÙˆÙ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªÙØµÙ„ Ù…Ù†Ø§Ø®ÙŠØ±.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\">ØªØ³ØªØºØ±Ù‚ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø­ÙˆØ§Ù„ÙŠ Ù¢ - Ù£ Ø³Ø§Ø¹Ø§Øª. ÙŠØªÙ… Ø§Ø³ØªØ¶Ø§ÙØ© Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±Ø¶Ù‰ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø³ØªØ´ÙÙ‰ Ù„Ù…Ø¯Ø© Ù„ÙŠÙ„Ø© ÙˆØ§Ø­Ø¯Ø© Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ©. ÙÙŠ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØŒ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬Ø§Øª ÙˆØ§Ù„ØªØ·Ø¨ÙŠÙ‚Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ø§Ø±Ø¯Ø© Ù„ØªØ³Ø±ÙŠØ¹ Ø§Ù„Ø´ÙØ§Ø¡. Ù…Ù† Ø£Ø¬Ù„ Ø­Ù…Ø§ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù†Ø§Ø·Ù‚ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø³Ø§Ø³Ø© Ù…Ø«Ù„ Ø§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø±ÙˆÙ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… ØŒ ÙŠØªÙ… ÙˆØ¶Ø¹ Ø¬Ø¨ÙŠØ±Ø© Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø¬Øµ Ø£Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ø¨Ù„Ø§Ø³ØªÙŠÙƒ ÙˆØ­Ø´Ø§ Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø³ÙŠÙ„ÙŠÙƒÙˆÙ† Ù…Ø¹ ÙˆØ¬ÙˆØ¯ Ø«Ù‚Ø¨ ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ù†ØªØµÙ. ØªØªÙ… Ø¥Ø²Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø­ÙØ§Ø¦Ø¸ Ø§Ù„Ø³ÙŠÙ„ÙŠÙƒÙˆÙ† Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ ÙŠÙˆÙ…ÙŠÙ† ØŒ ÙˆÙŠØªÙ… Ø¥Ø²Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø®ÙŠÙˆØ· Ø·Ø±Ù Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø¨Ø¹Ø¯ Ø³Ø¨Ø¹Ø© Ø£ÙŠØ§Ù… ØŒ ÙˆÙŠØ¹ÙˆØ¯ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø±ÙŠØ¶ Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø­ÙŠØ§ØªÙ‡ Ø§Ù„ÙŠÙˆÙ…ÙŠØ©.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Rhinoplastik','rhinoplastik',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Rhinoplastik ist eine Operation, die darauf abzielt, Deformit&auml;ten in der Nase zu l&ouml;sen und die psychologischen Auswirkungen, die mit diesen Problemen auftreten, zu korrigieren. Bei dieser Operation wird das Gesicht als Ganzes bewertet und entsprechend dem Gesichtsausdruck wird die am besten geeignete Intervention durchgef&uuml;hrt.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDie gesamte Krankengeschichte des Patienten wird auch vor der Operation zusammen mit Nasenproblemen ber&uuml;cksichtigt. Ob es eine andere innere St&ouml;rung in der Nase gibt, der allergische Zustand des Patienten, fr&uuml;here Operationen oder Gesichtsverletzungen werden detailliert bewertet. Angesichts all dieser Daten wird die f&uuml;r den Patienten am besten geeignete Methode ausgew&auml;hlt und angewendet. Die Operation kann mit offener oder geschlossener Technik durchgef&uuml;hrt werden. Knochen und Knorpel, die gekr&uuml;mmt sind und Probleme beim Atmen verursachen, werden entfernt, geformt und wieder in die Nase eingef&uuml;hrt. Bei der Operation werden Knorpel, Knochen in der Nase, B&auml;nder und Gewebe, die diese Strukturen zusammenhalten, so weit wie m&ouml;glich gesch&uuml;tzt. Wenn es auch ein Wachstum des Nasenfleisches oder einer Zyste gibt, die eine Verstopfung der Atmung verursacht, werden diese Pathologien auch gleichzeitig interveniert. Zusammenfassend ist die Rhinoplastik eine Operation, die eine pr&auml;zise chirurgische Akkumulation erfordert und sorgf&auml;ltig durchgef&uuml;hrt werden muss.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDie Operation wird durchgef&uuml;hrt, um die Nase neu zu gestalten und ein &auml;sthetisches Aussehen zu gew&auml;hrleisten, das mit dem Gesicht harmonisch ist. Mit dieser Operation kann die Nase verkleinert, der Winkel der Nase zur Oberlippe ver&auml;ndert, die Nasenspitze repariert und andere Defekte wie Einbuchtungen und Vorspr&uuml;nge in der Nase korrigiert werden. Die Septumstruktur wird begradigt, indem die Knochen und Knorpel korrigiert werden, die Ihre Nase formen. Das Septum ist die Struktur aus Knorpel und Knochen, die Ihre Nasenl&ouml;cher trennen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDie Operation dauert ca. 2-3 Stunden. Patienten werden 1 Nacht nach der Operation im Krankenhaus untergebracht. In diesem Prozess werden Behandlungen und kalte Anwendungen durchgef&uuml;hrt, die die Heilung beschleunigen. Um empfindliche Bereiche wie Knorpel und Knochen zu sch&uuml;tzen, wird eine Gipsschiene oder eine plastikschiene und ein Silikonpuffer mit einem Loch in der Mitte eingesetzt. Silikonpuffer werden nach 2 Tagen, Nasen-Stiche nach 7 Tagen entfernt und der Patient kehrt in seinen Alltag zur&uuml;ck.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'8a689bf177518d84bd3b20220407eyalcind4bf7a8abe98873054d2',7,'2022-04-07 15:14:29',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(30,43,'2022-04-07',NULL,'Septorinoplasti','septorinoplasti',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Burun ortasÄ±nda burun hava yolunu ikiye b&ouml;len, kemik ve kÄ±kÄ±rdaktan oluÅŸan yapÄ±ya septum denir. Septumda doÄŸumsal ya da edinilmiÅŸ olarak eÄŸiklikler oluÅŸabilir. DoÄŸumsal olan eÄŸikliklerin en sÄ±k sebebi zor doÄŸum ve doÄŸum travmasÄ±dÄ±r. EdinilmiÅŸ olan burun septum eÄŸiklikleri ise burun geliÅŸimi devam ederken oluÅŸan y&uuml;z travmalarÄ±dÄ±r. Burun ortasÄ±nda bulunan septumun eÄŸik olmasÄ± durumuna nazal septum deviasyonu denilmektedir ve bu durumun cerrahi olarak d&uuml;zeltilmesi iÅŸlemine septoplasti adÄ± verilir. Septorinoplasti iÅŸlemi ise burundaki ÅŸekil bozukluklarÄ± ile nefes alma problemlerini &ccedil;&ouml;zmeyi ve bu sorunlarla birlikte ortaya &ccedil;Ä±kan psikolojik etkileri de d&uuml;zeltmeyi ama&ccedil;layan bir operasyondur. Septoplasti ameliyatÄ±nda hem nefes almayÄ± engelleyen kemik eÄŸikliÄŸine m&uuml;dahale edilir (septoplasti) hem de y&uuml;z&uuml;n genel yapÄ±sÄ±na ve ifadesine g&ouml;re en uygun estetik m&uuml;dahale (rinoplasti) ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirilir.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHastanÄ±n t&uuml;m saÄŸlÄ±k ge&ccedil;miÅŸi de burun problemleriyle birlikte operasyon &ouml;ncesinde b&uuml;t&uuml;n olarak g&ouml;z &ouml;n&uuml;nde bulundurulur. Burunda baÅŸka i&ccedil; bozukluÄŸun olup olmadÄ±ÄŸÄ±; hastanÄ±n alerjik durumlarÄ±, daha &ouml;nce ge&ccedil;irdiÄŸi ameliyatlar veya y&uuml;z travmalarÄ± ayrÄ±ntÄ±lÄ± bir bi&ccedil;imde deÄŸerlendirilir. T&uuml;m bu veriler Ä±ÅŸÄ±ÄŸÄ±nda hasta i&ccedil;in en uygun olan y&ouml;ntem se&ccedil;ilir ve uygulanÄ±r. Operasyon a&ccedil;Ä±k ya da kapalÄ± teknikle yapÄ±labilir. EÄŸri olan ve nefes almada soruna neden olan kemik ve kÄ±kÄ±rdaklar &ccedil;Ä±karÄ±lÄ±r, ÅŸekil verilerek tekrar burun i&ccedil;erisine yerleÅŸtirilir. Operasyonda burun i&ccedil;erisinde kÄ±kÄ±rdak, kemik, bu yapÄ±larÄ± bir arada tutan baÄŸlar ve doku m&uuml;mk&uuml;n olduÄŸunca korunmaya &ccedil;alÄ±ÅŸÄ±lÄ±r. Kemik ve kÄ±kÄ±rdaÄŸÄ±n korunmayÄ±p t&uuml;m&uuml;n&uuml;n alÄ±nmasÄ± gibi bir durumda burun sÄ±rtÄ±nda &ccedil;&ouml;kmeler oluÅŸtuÄŸu semer burun deformitesi meydana gelir ve bu durumda ameliyat sonrasÄ± ÅŸekil bozukluÄŸu ve nefes alma problemlerinin devam etmesine neden olur. &Ouml;zet olarak Septorinoplasti hassas bir cerrahi birikim gerektiren ve titizlikle yapÄ±lmasÄ± gereken bir ameliyattÄ±r.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nOperasyon burnu yeniden ÅŸekillendirmek, y&uuml;zle uyumlu estetik bir g&ouml;r&uuml;n&uuml;m saÄŸlamak ve bunlarla birlikte burnun fonksiyonel sorunlarÄ±nÄ± da ortadan kaldÄ±rmak&nbsp; amacÄ±yla uygulanÄ±r. HastalarÄ±mla g&ouml;r&uuml;ÅŸmelerimde her zaman belirttiÄŸim &uuml;zere estetik olarak g&uuml;zel ancak nefes alamadÄ±ÄŸÄ±nÄ±z bir burun, ÅŸÄ±k ama ayaÄŸÄ±nÄ±zÄ± sÄ±kan bir ayakkabÄ±ya benzer. KullanamadÄ±ÄŸÄ±nÄ±z nefes alamadÄ±ÄŸÄ±nÄ±z bir burun ile yaÅŸamak ise &ccedil;ok eziyetlidir ve eninde sonunda revizyona gider. Bu operasyonla burun k&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;lt&uuml;lebilir; burnun &uuml;st dudak ile olan a&ccedil;Ä±sÄ± deÄŸiÅŸtirilebilir, burun ucu onarÄ±lÄ±p burundaki girinti, &ccedil;Ä±kÄ±ntÄ± gibi diÄŸer kusurlar d&uuml;zeltilebilir, burnunuza ÅŸeklini veren kemikler ve kÄ±kÄ±rdak &uuml;zerinde d&uuml;zeltme yapÄ±larak septum yapÄ±sÄ± d&uuml;zleÅŸtirilir. AyrÄ±ca nefes alma zorluÄŸuna sebep olan problemler tespit edilir. Bu problemlerin baÅŸÄ±nda kemik eÄŸikliÄŸi olan tarafÄ±n tersinde olan burun eti b&uuml;y&uuml;mesidir. Burun eti b&uuml;y&uuml;mesi de eÄŸer m&uuml;dahale edilmezse burun tÄ±kanÄ±klÄ±ÄŸÄ±nÄ±n devam etmesine neden olur ve mutlaka m&uuml;dahale edilmeyi gerektirir. Ben septoplasti ya da septorinoplasti ameliyatÄ± olacak olan hastalarÄ±mÄ±n hepsinin burun i&ccedil;i endoskopik deÄŸerlendirmelerini yapÄ±yorum, gerekirse bilgisayarlÄ± tomografi ile ileri g&ouml;r&uuml;nt&uuml;leme y&ouml;ntemlerine baÅŸvuruyorum ve mutlaka operasyon sÄ±rasÄ±nda burun etine de iÅŸlem ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtiriyorum. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operasyon yaklaÅŸÄ±k 2-3 saat s&uuml;rmektedir. Hastalar ameliyattan sonra 1 gece hastanede misafir edilir. Bu s&uuml;re&ccedil;te iyileÅŸmeyi hÄ±zlandÄ±rÄ±cÄ± tedaviler ve soÄŸuk uygulamalarÄ± yapÄ±lÄ±r. KÄ±kÄ±rdak ve kemikler gibi hassas b&ouml;lgeleri korumak adÄ±na al&ccedil;Ä± ve ortasÄ± delik olan bir silikon tampon konulur. Silikon tamponlar 2 g&uuml;n sonra, burun ucu dikiÅŸleri 7 g&uuml;n sonra alÄ±nÄ±r ve hasta g&uuml;nl&uuml;k yaÅŸamÄ±na d&ouml;ner.&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','Septorhinoplasty','septorhinoplasty',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>The structure that divides the nasal airway into two in the middle of the nose and consists of bone and cartilage is called the septum. Congenital or acquired curvature of the septum may occur. The most common cause of congenital curvatures is difficult birth and birth trauma. Acquired nasal septum curvatures are facial traumas that occur while the development of the nose continues. If the septum in the middle of the nose is curved, it is called nasal septum deviation, and the surgical correction of this condition is called septoplasty. Septorhinoplasty is an operation that aims to solve nasal deformities and breathing problems and to correct the psychological effects that occur with these problems. In septoplasty surgery, both the bone curvature that prevents breathing is intervened (septoplasty) and the most appropriate aesthetic intervention (rhinoplasty) is performed according to the general structure and expression of the face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The patient&#39;s entire health history, along with nasal problems, is considered as a whole before the operation. Whether there are other internal disorders in the nose; The patient&#39;s allergic conditions, previous surgeries or facial trauma are evaluated in detail. In the light of all these data, the most appropriate method for the patient is selected and applied. The operation can be performed with open or closed technique. Bone and cartilages that are curved and cause breathing problems are removed, shaped and placed back into the nose. In the operation, cartilage, bone, ligaments and tissue that hold these structures together are tried to be preserved as much as possible. In a situation where bone and cartilage are not preserved and all of them are removed, saddle nose deformity occurs in which collapses on the nasal dorsum occur, and in this case, deformity and breathing problems continue after the surgery. In summary, Septorhinoplasty is an operation that requires sensitive surgical accumulation and must be performed meticulously.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThe operation is performed to reshape the nose, to provide an aesthetic appearance compatible with the face and to eliminate the functional problems of the nose. As I always say in my interviews with my patients, a nose that is aesthetically beautiful but you can&#39;t breathe is like a stylish but tight-fitting shoe. Living with a nose that you cannot use and cannot breathe is very tormenting and eventually goes to revision. With this operation, the nose can be reduced; The angle of the nose with the upper lip can be changed, the tip of the nose is repaired and other defects such as indentation and protrusion in the nose can be corrected, the septum structure is straightened by correcting the bones and cartilage that shape your nose. In addition, problems that cause breathing difficulties are detected. At the beginning of these problems is the growth of the nasal flesh on the opposite side of the bone inclination. The enlargement of the nasal flesh also causes the continuation of nasal congestion if it is not intervened and it definitely requires intervention. I make intranasal endoscopic evaluations of all of my patients who will have septoplasty or septorhinoplasty surgery, if necessary, I apply advanced imaging methods with computed tomography, and I definitely perform operations on the concha during the operation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The operation takes about 2-3 hours. Patients are hosted in the hospital for 1 night after the operation. In this process, treatments that accelerate healing and cold applications are made. In order to protect sensitive areas such as cartilage and bones, a plaster and a silicone pad with a hole in the middle are placed. Silicone pads are removed after 2 days, nasal tip sutures are removed after 7 days and the patient returns to his daily life.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ø±Ø£Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ','content-1770827144-6070',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">ÙŠØ³Ù…Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ù‡ÙŠÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙƒÙˆÙ† Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ø¸Ø§Ù… ÙˆØ§Ù„ØºØ¶Ø§Ø±ÙŠÙ Ø§Ù„Ø°ÙŠ ÙŠÙ‚Ø³Ù… Ù…Ø¬Ø±Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ù‡ÙˆØ§Ø¡ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ù†ØµÙÙŠÙ† ÙÙŠ Ù…Ù†ØªØµÙ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø². Ù‚Ø¯ ØªØ­Ø¯Ø« Ø§Ù†Ø­Ø±Ø§ÙØ§Øª Ø®Ù„Ù‚ÙŠØ© Ø£Ùˆ Ù…ÙƒØªØ³Ø¨Ø© ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø². Ø§Ù„Ø³Ø¨Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø± Ø´ÙŠÙˆØ¹Ø§ Ù…Ù† Ø£Ø¨Ù„ÙŠÙ‚ÙˆØ³ Ø§Ù„Ø®Ù„Ù‚ÙŠØ© Ù‡Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù…Ù„ Ø§Ù„ØµØ¹Ø¨ ÙˆØµØ¯Ù…Ø© Ø§Ù„ÙˆÙ„Ø§Ø¯Ø©. Ø§Ù„Ø³Ø¨Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø£ÙƒØ«Ø± Ø´ÙŠÙˆØ¹Ù‹Ø§ Ù„Ù„Ø§Ù†Ø­Ø±Ø§Ù Ø§Ù„Ø®Ù„Ù‚ÙŠ Ù‡Ùˆ ØµØ¹ÙˆØ¨Ø© Ø§Ù„ÙˆÙ„Ø§Ø¯Ø© ÙˆØµØ¯Ù…Ø© Ø§Ù„ÙˆÙ„Ø§Ø¯Ø©. ØªÙ‚ÙˆØ³Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙƒØªØ³Ø¨Ø© Ù‡ÙŠ ØµØ¯Ù…Ø§Øª ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ¬Ù‡ ØªØ­Ø¯Ø« Ø£Ø«Ù†Ø§Ø¡ Ø§Ø³ØªÙ…Ø±Ø§Ø± ØªØ·ÙˆØ± Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù. ØªØ³Ù…Ù‰ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ÙŠÙ…ÙŠÙ„ ÙÙŠÙ‡Ø§ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙˆØ¬ÙˆØ¯ ÙÙŠ Ù…Ù†ØªØµÙ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù Ø¨Ø§Ù†Ø­Ø±Ø§Ù Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ ØŒ ÙˆØªØ³Ù…Ù‰ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„ØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­ÙŠ Ù„Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ù„Ø© Ø±Ø£Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ. Ø±Ø£Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ Ù‡Ùˆ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠØ© ØªÙ‡Ø¯Ù Ø¥Ù„Ù‰ Ø­Ù„ Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„ Ø§Ù„ØªÙ†ÙØ³ Ù…Ø¹ ØªØ´ÙˆÙ‡Ø§Øª ÙÙŠ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†Ù ÙˆØªØµØ­ÙŠØ­ Ø§Ù„Ø¢Ø«Ø§Ø± Ø§Ù„Ù†ÙØ³ÙŠØ© Ø§Ù„ØªÙŠ ØªØ­Ø¯Ø« Ù…Ø¹ Ù‡Ø°Ù‡ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø´Ø§ÙƒÙ„. ÙÙŠ Ø¬Ø±Ø§Ø­Ø© Ø±Ø£Ø¨ Ø§Ù„Ø­Ø§Ø¬Ø² Ø§Ù„Ø£Ù†ÙÙŠ ØŒ ÙŠØªÙ… Ø§Ù„ØªØ¯Ø®Ù„ Ù