ch. WaÌˆhrend es in beweglichen Bereichen wie der Lippenpartie 8-10 Monate verbleibt, betraÌˆgt die Haltbarkeit am Knochen 12-18 Monate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wie in jeder Arztpraxis werden nach der Feststellung der BeduÌˆrfnisse und des allgemeinen Gesundheitszustandes des Patienten die Bereiche bestimmt, die im Gesichtsbereich aufgefuÌˆllt werden muÌˆssen. Vor den FuÌˆllungsanwendungen werden AnaÌˆsthesiecremes verwendet, um das Schmerzempfinden des Patienten vollstaÌˆndig zu verhindern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die FuÌˆllungsanwendung ist ein sehr praktischer medizinischer Eingriff und es gibt keinen Heilungsprozess. Die Person kann sofort nach der Anwendung problemlos in ihr Leben zuruÌˆckkehren, aber es ist natuÌˆrlich, dass im Anwendungsbereich fuÌˆr einige Tage OÌˆdeme auftreten. Diese OÌˆdeme, leichten Schwellungen und RoÌˆtungen sind voruÌˆbergehend und normalisieren sich einige Tage nach der Anwendung vollstaÌˆndig.</p>\r\n','',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'d736f06edef210a411a120220407eyalcin036755c57063491d3c92',7,'2022-04-07 15:33:43',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(40,42,'2022-04-07',NULL,'GÃ¶z AltÄ± IÅŸÄ±k Dolgusu','gz-alt-ik-dolgusu',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Uykusuzluk, genetik etkenler, d&uuml;zensiz beslenme ve stresli hayat estetik sorunlarÄ± da beraberinde getirir. Bunlardan birisi de g&ouml;z altÄ±nda yaÅŸanan morluklar ve &ccedil;&ouml;kmelerdir. Bu sorunlarÄ±n tedavisinde g&ouml;z altÄ± Ä±ÅŸÄ±k dolgusu kullanÄ±lÄ±r.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dolgu uygulamalarÄ±nda kullanÄ±lan hyal&uuml;ronik asit, insan v&uuml;cudunda hali hazÄ±rda bulunan doÄŸal bir maddedir. DolgularÄ±n erime s&uuml;resi kullanÄ±lan dolgu &uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml;ne ve uygulanan b&ouml;lgeye g&ouml;re deÄŸiÅŸiklik g&ouml;sterir. G&ouml;z altÄ± gibi hareketin alt y&uuml;z b&ouml;lgesine g&ouml;re daha az olduÄŸu b&ouml;lgelerde 12-18 ay kadar kalÄ±cÄ±lÄ±k mevcuttur. Uygulama &ouml;ncesinde anestezi kremleri kullanÄ±larak hastanÄ±n aÄŸrÄ± duymasÄ± tamamen engellenir.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&ouml;z AltÄ± IÅŸÄ±k Dolgusu uygulamasÄ± olduk&ccedil;a pratik bir medikal m&uuml;dahaledir ve iyileÅŸme s&uuml;reci bulunmamaktadÄ±r. KiÅŸi uygulamanÄ±n hemen sonrasÄ±nda yaÅŸamÄ±na sorunsuzca geri d&ouml;nebilmektedir. Uygulama yapÄ±lan alanda birka&ccedil; g&uuml;n &ouml;dem olmasÄ± doÄŸaldÄ±r. Bu &ouml;demler, hafif ÅŸiÅŸkinlikler ve kÄ±zarÄ±klÄ±klar ge&ccedil;icidir ve uygulamadan birka&ccedil; g&uuml;n sonra tamamen normale d&ouml;necektir. Bu uygulama diÄŸer dolgu uygulamalarÄ±n aksine deri altÄ±na deÄŸil, kemik &uuml;zerine uygulanÄ±r.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&ouml;z altÄ± dolgu uygulamasÄ± iÄŸne ile yapÄ±labildiÄŸi gibi kan&uuml;l ile de ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirilir. Ben hastalarÄ±ma g&ouml;z altÄ± dolgu uygulamasÄ±nÄ± kan&uuml;lle ger&ccedil;ekleÅŸtirmekteyim. Kan&uuml;l, dolgu vermede kullanÄ±lan ucu k&uuml;nt bir aparattÄ±r. &nbsp;G&ouml;z &ccedil;evresi gibi aÄŸrÄ± a&ccedil;Ä±sÄ±ndan hassas ve damar y&ouml;n&uuml;nden zengin bir b&ouml;lgede, g&ouml;z altÄ± parlaklÄ±ÄŸÄ± istemi ile baÅŸvuran hastalara iÄŸne ile yapÄ±lan iÅŸlemler her zaman deÄŸil ama bazen aÄŸrÄ±lÄ± olabilir ve damarÄ±n iÄŸne ile hasarÄ± sonucu kanamaya baÄŸlÄ± uzun s&uuml;re morluÄŸa neden olabilir. Kan&uuml;l hem aÄŸrÄ± ve acÄ±yÄ± ortadan kaldÄ±rÄ±r hem de kanama riskini en aza indirir. Tecr&uuml;beli ellerde yapÄ±ldÄ±ÄŸÄ±nda sÄ±fÄ±r kanama ile 5 dakikayÄ± ge&ccedil;meyen bir iÅŸlemdir ve iÅŸlemden hemen sonra hasta g&uuml;nl&uuml;k rutinine d&ouml;nebilir.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ä°ÅŸlemden sonra 15 g&uuml;n boyunca bol su t&uuml;ketilmesi &ouml;nerilmektedir. 15 g&uuml;n sonra kontrol amacÄ±yla hasta tekrar deÄŸerlendirilir.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','Under Eye Light Filling','under-eye-light-filling',1,NULL,NULL,'<p>Insomnia, genetic factors, irregular diet and stressful life bring along aesthetic problems. One of them is bruises and collapses under the eyes. In the treatment of these problems, under-eye light filling is used.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hyaluronic acid, which is used in filling applications, is a natural substance already present in the human body. The melting time of the fillings varies according to the filling product used and the applied area. In areas where the movement is less than the lower face, such as under the eyes, there is a permanence of 12-18 months. Before the application, anesthetic creams are used to completely prevent the patient from feeling pain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Under-Eye Light Fill application is a very practical medical intervention and there is no recovery process. The person can return to his/her life without any problem immediately after the application. It is natural to have edema in the treated area for a few days. These edemas, mild swellings and redness are temporary and will completely return to normal a few days after the application. Unlike other filling applications, this application is applied on the bone, not under the skin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Under-eye filler can be applied with a needle as well as with a cannula. I perform the under-eye filler application to my patients with a cannula. The cannula is a blunt device used for filling. In an area that is sensitive to pain and rich in blood vessels, such as the area around the eyes, needle procedures may be painful sometimes, but not always, and may cause long-term bruising due to bleeding as a result of needle damage to the patients who apply with the request of under-eye brightness. The cannula both eliminates pain and suffering and minimizes the risk of bleeding. It is a procedure that does not exceed 5 minutes with zero bleeding when performed in experienced hands, and the patient can return to his daily routine immediately after the procedure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is recommended to consume plenty of water for 15 days after the procedure. After 15 days, the patient is re-evaluated for control purposes.</p>\r\n','','',NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'','','Ø­Ø´Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ø¶ÙˆØ¡ ØªØ­Øª Ø§Ù„Ø¹ÙŠÙ†ÙŠÙ†','content-1770827144-2601',1,NULL,NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\">Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø±Ù‚ ÙˆØ§Ù„Ø¹ÙˆØ§Ù…Ù„ Ø§Ù„ÙˆØ±Ø§Ø«ÙŠØ© ÙˆØ§Ù„Ù†Ø¸Ø§Ù… Ø§Ù„ØºØ°Ø§Ø¦ÙŠ ØºÙŠØ± Ø§Ù„